Specimens examined: Palau: Ulebsechel I. (paratypes, Ks 52 NMNH); N.W. Ulebsechel I. (light trap, alt. 25 m, male, Gr 52); Babelthuap I., E. Ngatpang (65 m, light trap, male, Gr 52 NMNH)
Unexamined MRSI specimens: Additional 16 collections, mostly males, by Be Dy Gr, 1947-54, from: Palau: Babelthuap I., Koror I., Ulebsechel I.
